  76,1,Is there not a period of time when each human is nothing yet worth mentioning
  76,2,"ЋєForЋЇ indeed, We ЋєaloneЋЇ created humans from a drop of mixed fluids,¬†Ћєin orderЋЇ to test them, so We made them hear and see"
  76,3,"We already showed them the Way, whether they Ћєchoose toЋЇ be grateful or ungrateful"
  76,4,"Indeed, We have prepared for the disbelievers chains, shackles, and a blazing Fire"
